    narr:generatedFrom "fbecaf3eb87d0cdfcd9a65d3a418d1aa5bd8cdef" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs the evolving lexicon and rhetorical architecture of Aswritten. The narrative trajectory is anchored by foundational positioning phrases like [narrative as steering vector](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_SteeringVector), [worldview as code](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_WorldviewAsCode), and the promise to [think like your org](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_ThinkLikeYourOrg). Over time, the opening hook has shifted from enterprise-centric framing toward [the hallucination question](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_Hallucinating) and [context engineering](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_ContextEngineering) as the primary competitive reframe. The company’s voice is characterized by a high-conviction idiolect, utilizing [antithesis/reframe constructions](narr:StyleObs_VerbatimReframe) (not-X-it's-Y) and [Clojure-framed architectural metaphors](narr:StyleObs_ClojureIdiolect). Key product terms such as [collective memory](narr:Observation_KeyPhrases_1), [lens drafting](narr:StyleObs_LensDraftingTerm), and [micro-telltale](narr:StyleObs_LensMicroTelltale) recur as load-bearing taxonomy. The documentation also captures Scarlet’s specific idiolect, including [archery metaphors](narr:StyleObs_5) and [meta-transparency devices](narr:StyleObs_10) like conviction labels, which serve to ground abstract claims in epistemic honesty. The hub also documents the [information vs. perspective distinction](narr:Obs_InformationVsPerspective) and the [consensus-view prompt](narr:Obs_EVConsensusAnswerQuote) as critical operational heuristics.""" ;
